I have had good luck with them.  Others have reported serious problems in
terms of support and quality control.  I've done business with them for a
few years and had no problems.  One warning: they are very hard to reach;
their phone system is overloaded and the voice-mail system sometimes takes 
you in circles.  They say they are working on this.  Also they are changing
to a new order-entry computer system, which has played hell with their
response time.

